txt.en: 'I knew you would not be able to resist sweet revenge, Jajax.'
'Look closely at your men. This is what becomes of Corsairs who forsake the Way.'
'Now you and your little outsider friend will die with them!'
'I have sent words to the other captains of your betrayal, Jajax.'
'They will come for you. If I fail to kill you, they will not. You and your outsider friend!'
